data.description: Equity building homeowner? Renovator? This home is perfect for both! This all brick home in the Indian Hills neighborhood with 2942 sq/ft total, needs some cosmetic love with some updating, so the home is priced accordingly.  The A/C was upgraded in 2019 and the furnace was installed in 2014 as was the water heater. Service Guard serviced the HVAC in 2022. The roof is only 4 years old, and the foundation is solid. The home sits on 1/4 acre in town, and on a corner. Set your appointment to see what you can do to build equity or invest in your next project.
